						               													<description>Be the fastest to find a word that meets all 3 conditions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For lovers of word games, comes this super agile proposal to train mental skills and vocabulary. A game where participants play simultaneously, trying to be the first to say a word that complies the given conditions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For an easier game or to play with children, you can play with two or one of the categories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SETUP&amp;#10;Shuffle the 3 condition decks separatedly and reveal the top card from each one.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAMEPLAY&amp;#10;Each round, players try simultaneously to say a word that complies with the 3 conditions. The first player to find that word, gains 1 point and take one of the 3 cards of their choice, and replace it with the top one of the correspondent deck. Then the next round begins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The same word can't be used again during the next 3 rounds.&amp;#10;The same category can't be replaced twice in a row.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;END OF GAME&amp;#10;The first player to reach 10 points, wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
